# ////////////// #
# /// maxsim /// #
# ////////////// #


# TOPIC MODEL

The model used to calculate topic similarity is the biterm topic model.


# DATA SET

The model is based on titles of research publications filed in MPG.PuRe.
A snapshot of the repository data was taken on Dec 1, 2019.
The final selection consists of 221,717 publications.


# MEMORY USAGE

To install this package, you need at least 4.5 GB of free RAM.
To use this package, you need at least 2 GB of free RAM.


# INSTALLATION

$ R
> devtools::install_gitlab("herreio/maxsim")


# DOCUMENTATION

$ R
> help(package="maxsim")
